Oh, that's mine.

00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:41.069
Yes, thank you.

00:01:41.070 --> 00:01:42.810
Thank you. Have a good one.

00:01:43.270 --> 00:01:45.640
Thank you, ma'am. Thanks again.

